// Personal signing override. Copy this file to `local.xcconfig` (which is
// gitignored) and replace the values with your own. The wisp target's
// DEVELOPMENT_TEAM and PRODUCT_BUNDLE_IDENTIFIER will pick up your overrides
// without you having to re-enter them in Xcode after every merge or pull.
//
// To find your DEVELOPMENT_TEAM:
//   - Xcode → Settings → Accounts → click your Apple ID → click Manage
//     Certificates / View Details, the Team ID is shown next to the team name.
//   - Or run `security find-identity -v -p codesigning` in Terminal and look
//     for the parenthesized ID after "Apple Development: …".
//
// PRODUCT_BUNDLE_IDENTIFIER must be unique to your team — Personal Teams
// won't sign someone else's bundle id.

DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = ABCDEFGHIJ
PRODUCT_BUNDLE_IDENTIFIER = yourname.wisp
